The paper focuses on salient object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves using color names and attention maps, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions using post-processing techniques to improve the saliency maps, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) subcategories.
